elements.name: TS_RegisteredCheckout_05 - Registered User of 6thstreet.com site should be able to place order using TabbyPayInInstallments

steps.name: User clicks on login link
User enters valid login details "validuser" username and "validuser" password in the login popup
User clicks on login button
user login is successfull
Home page is displayed
User clears cart
user enters product name as "DSW425730-230-NUDE" in search text box and click search icon
user clicks on product tile in result
user selects countrySize as "EU", size as "41"
user clicks on ADDTOBAG button
user navigates to shopping bag page and clicks on proceedToCheckout button
user enters the valid details for "uae" shipping address
user selects payment option as "TabbyPayInInstallments"
user clicks on place order button
user fills all tabby details
Order placing should be successful
user clicks on my account top menu
user selects order history option
order history page is displayed
verify order status in history to be "processing"
click on view order
Verify order status in details to be "processing"
Verify order payment in details to be "Pay in installments"
Launch Tabby Merchant URL "https://merchant.tabby.ai/auth"
User enters merchant valid login details "merchantuser" username and "merchantuser" password in the login popup
User clicks on merchant login button
User inputs tabby order number in merchant page
Verify country "ARE" status "New" order
Launch Admin Magento URL "https://6thadmin-stage.6tst.com/sixadmin"
User enters magento valid login details "magentouser" username and "magentouser" password in the login popup
User clicks on magento login button
user should be landed into Magento dashboard
user clicks on sales module
